| 【内层 CURRENT DIAGNOSTICS】     | NUMBER | ROW_COUNT | RETURNED_SQLSTATE | MESSAGE_TEXT                               |
+----------------------------------+--------+-----------+-------------------+--------------------------------------------+
| 【内层 CURRENT DIAGNOSTICS】     |      1 |        -1 | 42S02             | Table 'test.no_such_table43' doesn't exist |
+----------------------------------+--------+-----------+-------------------+--------------------------------------------+
SELECT '【内层 STACKED DIAGNOSTICS】',@num2 'NUMBER', @row2 'ROW_COUNT',@sta2 'RETURNED_SQLSTATE', @msg2 'MESSAGE_TEXT';//
